<!-- Application Modal Container -->
<div class="submission-modal-overlay submission-modal-hidden" data-application-modal-target="container"
    data-action="click->application-modal#closeOnOutsideClick keydown@window->application-modal#closeOnEscape"
    aria-hidden="true" role="dialog">
  
  <div class="submission-modal-content">
    <button data-action="click->application-modal#hide" class="submission-modal-close-button">×</button>
    <section>
      <h4>🎧 Apply to Sell Your Sounds on Bamsfx</h4>
      <p>We’re opening <strong>Bamsfx.com</strong> to a select group of sound designers who want to sell their <strong>sound effect packs</strong> — and optionally <strong>individual tracks</strong> that can be included in user-created collections.</p>
      <p>If you're passionate about sound and want to join a platform built specifically for sound designers, we’d love to hear from you!</p>

      <hr>

      <h4>🔒 What You’re Agreeing To</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>✅ You keep 70% of the revenue after fees and VAT.</li>
        <li>✅ You grant Bamsfx a non-exclusive license to distribute your content.</li>
        <li>✅ You remain the legal owner and are responsible for your sounds and images.</li>
        <li>✅ You can choose to sell full packs only, or also offer individual tracks that can be purchased in collections.</li>
        <li>✅ You can request removal of your content at any time; previously sold items remain downloadable to buyers.</li>
      </ul>

      <hr>

      <h4>📝 How to Apply</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>1. Fill out your full name and contact email so we can get in touch.</li>
        <li>2. Let us know if you want to sell just full packs, or also individual tracks and allow them in collections.</li>
        <li>3. Share up to 5 links to your work so we can review your sound quality and style.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>We're looking for designers who bring <strong>quality, originality, and creativity</strong> to the platform.</p>
      <p>If that’s you, apply now and let’s build something great together!</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>